    v1.8.8 "Atlas" (Workstream B): in-app i18n. English (default) string catalog.

    Scope of this first externalization pass (per the WS B plan): the primary UI
    surfaces — the in-game control bar, the Settings sheet labels/headers, the
    About + onboarding dialogs, and the Language picker. Deeper / rarer strings
    (per-pad remap UI, netplay status lines, transient status toasts) keep their
    literals for now and are tagged TODO(i18n) at their call sites; they fall back
    to English regardless until translated. The matching values-es/strings.xml
    holds the Spanish translations (reused from the desktop ADR-0023 catalog where
    the strings line up).
-->
